00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:26,640
I could let it go down the drain. I don't care.

579
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,920
That was always the plan.

580
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:30,599
But I didn't expect you to get lucky.

581
00:33:30,720 --> 00:33:32,359
Martin was still willing to help you.

582
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:33,599
Too bad

583
00:33:34,599 --> 00:33:37,599
he won't be around much longer either.

584
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,880
He'll outlive you.

585
00:33:42,039 --> 00:33:42,920
Without Martin,

586
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:44,920
just you and that cook,

587
00:33:45,599 --> 00:33:46,440
sorry,

588
00:33:46,599 --> 00:33:48,720
at the time, I had no hope

589
00:33:48,720 --> 00:33:50,119
for Penglexuan's development.

590
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:51,720
Cut the crap.

591
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:53,000
Are you selling out or not?

592
00:33:53,039 --> 00:33:54,640
Yes, of course I'm selling.

593
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:56,160
My goal has been achieved.

594
00:33:56,319 --> 00:33:57,880
And this project is too risky.

595
00:33:57,880 --> 00:33:58,720
Why wouldn't I sell?

596
00:33:58,720 --> 00:34:00,039
Then hurry up.

597
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,759
According to the original agreement,

598
00:34:03,039 --> 00:34:04,039
how the buyback happens

599
00:34:04,519 --> 00:34:05,640
is up to me.

600
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:07,720
Name your price.

601
00:34:08,639 --> 00:34:10,440
For Jenny's sake,

602
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,760
and considering our relationship,

603
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:14,880
I won't ask for much.

604
00:34:15,079 --> 00:34:16,880
A flat price: thirty million.

605
00:34:17,079 --> 00:34:17,960
Are you insane?

606
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:27,039
Thirty million?

607
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,800
Is he out of his mind?

608
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:32,800
He only invested ten million total with us!

609
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:34,239
That's a twenty million profit in and out!

610
00:34:34,239 --> 00:34:35,360
He's robbing us!

611
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,800
That's exactly what he's doing now!

612
00:34:40,599 --> 00:34:42,480
Forget that we don't even have thirty million right now,

613
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:44,440
even if we did, we wouldn't give it to that bastard!

614
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,360
No matter what,

615
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,639
I must get him out.

616
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:50,880
Wait, Lianbao.

617
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,320
Don't get so worked up yet.

618
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:53,199
Weiguo,

619
00:34:53,199 --> 00:34:55,119
other than forcing him out,

620
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:57,239
do we have any other options?

621
00:34:58,559 --> 00:34:59,800
According to the agreement,

622
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:01,360
if we want to force him out,

623
00:35:01,559 --> 00:35:03,400
right now we can only agree to his demands.

624
00:35:05,559 --> 00:35:06,440
Just thinking about

625
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:07,800
working for him in the future,

626
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:09,199
every penny Penglexuan earns

627
00:35:09,199 --> 00:35:10,320
still having to give him a cut,

628
00:35:11,039 --> 00:35:12,519
I can't stand it.

629
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,199
Lianbao.

630
00:35:14,559 --> 00:35:16,199
A little impatience spoils great plans.

631
00:35:16,239 --> 00:35:18,199
Anger is a major taboo in business.

632
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,679
I know what you want to say,

633
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:21,000
but I don't want to hear it right now.

634
00:35:23,119 --> 00:35:25,639
This Kevin, as darn it as he is,

635
00:35:25,960 --> 00:35:27,280
he's not wrong in what he did.

636
00:35:27,639 --> 00:35:28,800
He just did what a businessman

637
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:29,880
is supposed to do:

638
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:31,920
maximize his own commercial value.

639
00:35:32,039 --> 00:35:32,760
I think

640
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:35,760
first, you need to separate the Honeycomb issue.

641
00:35:36,039 --> 00:35:37,559
Kevin is right about this.

642
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:39,239
The equity is in your hands,

643
00:35:39,239 --> 00:35:40,920
but without his resources,

644
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:42,440
that equity is basically worthless.

645
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:44,199
So what he did

646
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,559
is, relatively speaking, helping you get out of a bind.

647
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:48,239
So according to you,

648
00:35:48,239 --> 00:35:49,559
I should thank him?

649
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,360
Objectively speaking, yes.

650
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:54,039
As for how much money he makes with that equity,

651
00:35:54,039 --> 00:35:56,079
that's his business, not yours.

652
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:58,320
Our Penglexuan is just starting out.

653
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,800
There's no need to burn bridges with him.

654
00:36:00,199 --> 00:36:01,440
Wait until our Penglexuan

655
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,800
is strong and thriving,

656
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,320
then it won't be too late to challenge him.

657
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:06,119
I won't accept it.

658
00:36:06,239 --> 00:36:06,760
Lianbao.

659
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:09,000
Alright, alright, I know everything you say is right.

660
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:10,320
I also know you mean well for me.

661
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:11,119
Thank you.

662
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,800
But no matter the cost,

663
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:15,559
I must get Old Kai out.

664
00:36:15,559 --> 00:36:17,320
This isn't just a business matter.

665
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:19,320
It's personal between him and me.

666
00:36:19,880 --> 00:36:20,360
Lianbao.

667
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,000
Alright, alright.

668
00:36:21,639 --> 00:36:23,360
This isn't just a spur-of-the-moment impulse for me.

669
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:25,199
I've thought it through carefully.

670
00:36:25,559 --> 00:36:27,440
After Dong Qian's money comes in,

671
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:29,639
the shares Old Kai holds will double in value anyway.

672
00:36:30,039 --> 00:36:31,760
If we buy those shares back now,

673
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:33,800
our stake in Penglexuan will be larger.

674
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,800
In the future, those shares

675
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:36,360
will definitely be worth more than they are now.

676
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:39,000
I understand, but

677
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,559
we can't be so optimistic about things.

678
00:36:40,559 --> 00:36:42,039
We have to consider the worst-case scenario first.

679
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:45,000
If I let him keep walking all over me,

680
00:36:45,039 --> 00:36:47,039
the rest of my life might as well be dead.

681
00:36:47,119 --> 00:36:48,760
That is the worst outcome.

682
00:36:56,199 --> 00:36:57,360
I'm back!

683
00:37:06,159 --> 00:37:07,719
Why haven't you eaten?

684
00:37:08,039 --> 00:37:10,480
I'm talking to you.

685
00:37:11,159 --> 00:37:13,320
I'm working on the script right now.

686
00:37:13,559 --> 00:37:14,599
No time for that.

687
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,800
Your, uh...

688
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:17,400
Put it in the fridge.

689
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,840
I'll eat it in a bit.

690
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,960
It's not just today, is it?

691
00:37:21,599 --> 00:37:23,280
It's been several days now.

692
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:24,960
What's going on with you?

693
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:26,039
If you're not feeling well,

694
00:37:26,039 --> 00:37:27,400
I'll take you to the hospital.

695
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,519
No, no, don't.

696
00:37:28,519 --> 00:37:29,840
Stop, I'm fine.

697
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,800
I'm begging you, okay?

698
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:34,039
I'm begging you, don't disturb me.

699
00:37:36,039 --> 00:37:37,039
These past few days,

700
00:37:37,039 --> 00:37:38,920
you've been staying up late every night.

701
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:41,599
You get up at dawn and start writing again.

702
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:44,079
Are you trying to ruin your health?

703
00:37:44,840 --> 00:37:46,039
Stop writing.

704
00:37:46,239 --> 00:37:47,679
You need to eat properly.

705
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,360
See, see?

706
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,480
All my inspiration,

707
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:53,079
you've just chattered it all away.

708
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:55,559
Old lady, listen to me.

709
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:58,360
The production company,

710
00:37:58,400 --> 00:38:01,199
they're meeting me in a couple of days.

711
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,840
I'll just write for a little while, okay?

712
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:03,719
Just a little while.

713
00:38:06,039 --> 00:38:08,559
Qiu'er isn't short of work.

714
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:13,800
Where did you get that idea?

715
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:16,480
I'm not writing for his sake.

716
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:17,960
I'm doing it for myself.

717
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:20,480
Don't think I don't know.

718
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:23,480
Before Qiu'er quit his job,

719
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:25,480
you weren't writing like this,

720
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:27,440
day and night.

721
00:38:30,599 --> 00:38:33,760
Our Qiu'er is being so stubborn now,

722
00:38:34,159 --> 00:38:37,239
isn't it just to keep us old folks from worrying?

723
00:38:37,239 --> 00:38:37,960
Isn't that right?

724
00:38:38,719 --> 00:38:40,760
You know how hard it is to find a job now.

725
00:38:41,559 --> 00:38:44,079
Plus, our Qiu'er is too picky.

726
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:46,719
And on top of that, they're about to have a baby.

727
00:38:46,719 --> 00:38:48,440
It's so hard.

728
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,840
Just a little writing, a little writing.

729
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:52,960
Aren't there his brothers?

730
00:38:52,960 --> 00:38:54,559
He won't suffer.

731
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,960
You, don't be like this.

732
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,320
Just eat your meal properly.

733
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:00,480
Come eat first, okay?

734
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:04,559
I know my own condition.

735
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,480
Let me tell you,

736
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:08,840
I just want to finish the first few episodes.

737
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:11,000
Finish them and sign the contract.

738
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,440
Once the contract is signed,

739
00:39:13,679 --> 00:39:15,440
the deposit will come through.

740
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:16,000
Aren't you...

741
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:17,320
...feeling more at ease now?

742
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:17,840
Right?

743
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:18,840
Just a bit of writing, a bit.

744
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:19,559
That's still not okay.

745
00:39:19,559 --> 00:39:20,079
No, no.

746
00:39:20,639 --> 00:39:22,440
Alright, promise me one thing.

747
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:25,440
Don't you dare tell our son about this.

748
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:28,400
He's having such a hard time, too much pressure.

749
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:30,559
Deal?

750
00:39:30,559 --> 00:39:31,039
No.

751
00:39:31,039 --> 00:39:32,840
You absolutely must not tell Qiu'er.

752
00:39:32,840 --> 00:39:33,440
Do you hear me?

753
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:35,719
He's under way too much pressure right now.

754
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:37,760
Okay?

755
00:39:38,679 --> 00:39:40,079
Fine.

756
00:39:40,199 --> 00:39:42,320
Let's eat first. I'll heat up the food.

757
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:44,840
I never thought you still loved me this much.

758
00:40:15,079 --> 00:40:18,159
Isn't it just to keep us old folks from worrying?

759
00:40:18,159 --> 00:40:19,039
Isn't that right?

760
00:40:19,679 --> 00:40:21,800
You know how hard it is to find a job now.

761
00:40:22,559 --> 00:40:25,079
Plus, our Qiu'er is too picky.

762
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:27,679
And on top of that, they're about to have a baby.

763
00:40:27,679 --> 00:40:29,440
It's so hard.

764
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:45,599
Hello, this is Tong Qiu.

765
00:40:45,599 --> 00:40:46,800
I interviewed with your company.

766
00:40:46,800 --> 00:40:47,599
May I trouble you to ask,

767
00:40:47,599 --> 00:40:49,159
do you have a result yet?

768
00:40:49,239 --> 00:40:50,400
Are you crazy?

769
00:40:50,679 --> 00:40:52,239
What time is it to be asking this?

770
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:53,639
Don't I need to sleep?

771
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:54,920
You don't even understand basic courtesy.

772
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:55,920
How could I hire you?

773
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:56,840
I'm sorry.
